        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=Please scan the entire json payload below under \"PAYLOAD\", not just the preview or snippet, for the parties array of each call object and return the \"CALL DETAILS\". Review the TASK LISTS data to get the corresponding task_list_id based on the customer_name and the list name.\n\nPlease format it in JSON like the \"OUTPUT JSON\" section and respond with NOTHING except the JSON.\n\nCALL DETAILS\n1. call ID\n2. title \n3. customer_name (infer this from non-bigpanda.io emails and call titles. Note: Upbound and Rent-A-Center are the same customer.)\n4. task_list_id\n5. speaker_map (an array mapping all speakerIds to their names from the \"parties\" array)\n\nTASK LISTS\n{{ $json.lists.toJsonString() }}\n\nOUTPUT JSON\n{\n  \"calls\": [\n    {\n       \"id\": \"xxxx\",\n       \"title\": \"...\",\n       \"customer_name\": \"...\",\n       \"task_list_id\": \"xxxx\",\n       \"speaker_map\": [\n         {\n            \"speakerId\": \"...\",\n            \"name\": \"...\"\n         },\n         {\n            \"speakerId\": \"...\",\n            \"name\": \"...\"\n         }\n       ]\n    },\n    {\n      ...\n     }\n  ]\n}\n\nPAYLOAD\n{{ $('Format call data').item.json.calls.toJsonString() }}"
